com.robopupu.api.plugin

Interface PluginStateComponent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PluginComponent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Feature, Interactor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFeature, AbstractFeaturePresenter, AbstractInteractor, AbstractListModel, AbstractModel, AbstractPluginStateComponent, AbstractPresenter, GraphInteractor, StateMachineInteractor

    public interface PluginStateComponent
extends PluginComponent
    PluginStateComponent extends PluginComponent to define an interface for plugin components that maintain PluginState.
